summary: This document is a certificate from the Department of Transportation certifying the authenticity of records related to the Krystone Helicopter S-76C, including its registration details. It is signed by Michelle Endsley, a Supervisory Legal Instruments Examiner, and Kevin TeAest, the Acting Manager of the Aircraft Registration Branch.

persons.name: Michelle Endsley
persons.context: Michelle Endsley is identified as the legal custodian of the aircraft records and signed the certificate of true copy.

persons.name: Kevin TeAest
persons.context: Kevin TeAest is mentioned as the Acting Manager who affixed the seal of the Department of Transportation to the certificate.

keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records related to the Krystone Helicopter S-76C.
The registration number of the helicopter is N722JE.
The certificate was signed on August 23, 2021.
Michelle Endsley is the legal custodian of the aircraft records.
The document is subject to a protective order.
